26 18-11-901. Title.
27 This subchapter shall be known and may be cited as the "Private
28 Property Protection Act".
29
30 18-11-902. Legislative findings and intent.
31 (a) The General Assembly finds that:
32 (1) The General Assembly has the highest interest in vindicating
33 and protecting private property rights; and
34 (2) The constitutional right to acquire, possess, and protect
35 property under Arkansas Constitution, Article 2, § 2, also embodies the
36 notion of the fundamental right to use property, including the use of
